{
  "stem": "25938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Culture And-- but then I-- I was under the influence of the-- of the leftist organizations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was actually-- in my little town 2/3 of my life in Europe, I mean, in Poland, I-- I lived in-- I did live in my little town.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest I did spend in other towns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to-- to-- I went to a little town near Jeziory to see [INAUDIBLE] I was in [POLISH], a few-- few places.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I-- now when I look back in retrospect, I see that-- I feel that we were actually-- we were second-rate or third-rate citizens then.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no Jewish-- Jewish clerks in the post office or in the-- somewhere there was no police, there was no-- we had-- we had one Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Doiste ?] was a volunteer in the Polish army against the saboteurs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was an exception.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Jewish people lived, they were-- they were-- they had trades, blacksmiths and tailors and stores.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't have-- people didn't have any jobs, government jobs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was-- it was tough to make a living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on this-- under these circumstances, the many-- there was an organization, the Bund, a Socialist Jewish party.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very, very influential in Poland, very popular.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was under-- under the influence of the-- of the literature on Marxism.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I-- then I-- I would say I was disappointed in all these things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When did you become disappointed?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When did you become disillusioned?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I read the-- the-- the trials in Soviet Russia, I guess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the Trotskyites, all the-- the-- all of the opponents of Stalin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then I said, must be something wrong with that.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
